The paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for intrusion detection in industrial control systems, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper specifically focuses on online learning algorithms, which are commonly used in machine learning (cs.LG) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the use of cost-sensitive learning, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and network security (cs.NI).
